                            oc:textContent "This skill enables image analysis, scene understanding, text extraction, and multi-frame comparison using OpenAI's vision-capable GPT models (e.g., `gpt-4o`, `gpt-4o-mini`). It supports single images, multiple images for comparison, and sequential frames for temporal analysis." ] ;
